  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Be between the ages of 2 and 12, inclusive

          -  Be healthy, with no illness that, in the judgment of the investigator or examining
             dentist, would interfere with the conduct of the test

          -  Be currently, and have been for at least three months immediately prior to the start
             of the study, brushing (or being brushed by care giver) their teeth on a daily basis

          -  Have parent/guardian complete and return the consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Have diabetes

          -  Be on dialysis

          -  Have an oral health condition that, in judgment of investigator or study medical
             personnel, could interfere with the conduct of the study.

          -  Wear metal braces

          -  Have an incomplete or missing consent form
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
